title: Dainville-Bertheléville
text: Dainville-Bertheléville () is a <a href="Communes%20of%20France">commune</a> in the <a href="Meuse%20%28department%29">Meuse</a> <a href="Departments%20of%20France">department</a> in <a href="Grand%20Est">Grand Est</a> in north-eastern <a href="France">France</a>.
